@node SQUAN "Squandered Resources"

@{b}Squandered Resources@{ub}

Color   = Black/Green
Rarity  = VI(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = BG
Artist  = Romas Kukalis

Text(VI): Sacrifice a land: Add to your mana pool one mana of any type the
