@node SULEI "Suleiman's Legacy"

@{b}Suleiman's Legacy@{ub}

Color   = Red/White
Rarity  = VI(R)
Type    = Enchantment
Cost    = RW
Artist  = Kaja Foglio

Text(VI): When Suleiman's Legacy comes into play, bury all Djinns and Efreets.
